Package: treasury.gov
Title: US Treasury Fiscal Data API Client for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the Treasury Fiscal Data API. Access
    debt, interest rates, exchange rates, revenue, spending, cash balances,
    securities, and auctions. Auto-types columns from API metadata.
